type: Superalgos Review - A city within a jungle

definition.text: Technical analysis is hard, so is Superalgos.

translations.text: Технический анализ сложен, как и Superalgos.

paragraphs.text: There is a jungle of crypto communities out there, Superalgos feels like the first city with working plumbing.
There is great detail taken to make sure (if you are patient) that you get over the learning curve to professional technical analysis.
It helps to have a large monitor!
